titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: PMS2 IMMUNOHISTOCHEMISTRY NUCLEAR EXPRESSION INTACT INDICATION CODE - Description

body.p: PMS2 IMMUNOHISTOCHEMISTRY NUCLEAR EXPRESSION INTACT INDICATION CODE is the same as attribute IMMUNOHISTOCHEMISTRY NUCLEAR EXPRESSION INTACT INDICATION CODE .

PMS2 IMMUNOHISTOCHEMISTRY NUCLEAR EXPRESSION INTACT INDICATION CODE is an indication of whether the PMS2 (PMS1 homolog 2) immunohistochemistry nuclear expression is intact during a Cancer Care Spell .
